  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>When you would encounter a follower of your Patron you must gather the knowledge they have and share it with your Patron by the end of the same day you gain that knowledge. If the follower is a part of a group, you only need to communicate and gather the knowledge from one. Sharing this knowledge with anyone before your Patron would result in an intense bout of Pain from your curse seal, giving you 3 ranks of either Bruised, Weakened, or Concussed, until you complete your next long rest (Patrons Choice)</p><p>If you would resist this Order, you begin to suffer bouts of short-term memory loss. Intelligence Checks you make are always made at disadvantage until you comply with this Order.</p>",
